This paper is about testing software, which is a topic that falls under software engineering (cs.SE). The use of combinatorial testing techniques is also relevant to software development (cs.SD). The paper discusses the creation of test suites, which is related to programming languages (cs.PL). The evaluation of the test suites in terms of fault detection and code coverage is relevant to systems and control (cs.SY). Finally, the use of automated techniques for testing is also relevant to artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
